(nc) put (pp) hand on the Dragon’s. ''I think it’s very
brave to admit that you’re scared,'' (sp) said.
''But it’s embarrassing!'' said the Dragon, staring at
the ground. ''I’ve always wanted to travel and see

wood. I’m afraid to fly over it and the thought of
walking through it gives me the heebie-jeebies!''
''Don’t worry, I’ll help you through the wood,'' said
(nc).
''Come on,'' (sp) smiled, ''let’s be brave.''
